criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Both male and female, aged 18 or older;

          -  Intact parathyroid hormone(iPTH) is more than 9 times the upper limit of the normal
             range (about 600pg/ml), with hypercalcemia or hyperphosphatemia;

          -  Refractory to medical therapy;

          -  Provided written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Primary or tertiary hyperparathyroidism;

          -  Familial hyperparathyroidism (MENⅠ, MENⅡ, hereditary HPT);

          -  Neck surgical exploration history;

          -  Parathyroid malignant tumor.
